Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.85,0:00:23.73,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界上擷取你的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.34,0:00:29.89,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著舞動的燈光  至今無法忘懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.97,0:00:35.23,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ahh  去把謎團解開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.44,0:00:43.49,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你仍然  充滿疑惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.61,0:00:51.62,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朋友一起度過每一天 直到將來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.87,0:00:58.80,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流著眼淚  無法釋懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.63,0:01:09.43,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想請教  如何追回失去的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.69,0:01:16.69,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界上擷取你的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.40,0:01:22.86,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著舞動的燈光  至今無法忘懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.99,0:01:28.03,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ahh  去把謎團解開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.16,0:01:33.00,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去把謎團解開吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.55,0:22:09.63,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何我們兩人會相遇?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.94,0:22:18.28,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起共看如此淒涼的夕陽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.90,0:22:25.75,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜索枯陽找尋能吸引他的話語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.42,0:22:34.67,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻找不出分離仍能相聚的安慰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.99,0:22:43.14,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉色雖然有時難看只要能以笑臉拂去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.38,0:22:51.73,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然爭執偶而有之但是也能忍耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.64,0:23:01.40,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要唯一的願望可以實現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.77,0:23:10.04,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經受傷的內心也將再度痊癒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.17,0:00:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛逝的秒針 閃耀的流星 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.87,0:00:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現代社會中疲憊的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.41,0:00:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南的推理是一帖良藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.46,0:00:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的事件是稍微不同的顏色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.09,0:00:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有刺的花是怎麼樣的花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.88,0:00:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.33,0:00:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.32,0:00:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.39,0:00:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.84,0:01:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界藝術大獎授獎紀念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.38,0:01:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個獎這麼了不起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.01,0:01:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.51,0:01:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是女明星青地麻理香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.44,0:02:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喏 那是足球隊的高田教練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.32,0:02:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 難看死了 別丟人了好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.96,0:02:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.37,0:02:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這裏的都是藝人還有運動選手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.34,0:02:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是名人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.28,0:02:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.25,0:02:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把我當什麼人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.69,0:02:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你放手聽到沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.59,0:02:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是被邀請來這兒的還敢抓我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.71,0:02:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔           爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.32,0:02:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.18,0:02:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我天下第一名偵探毛利小五郎都不認得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.38,0:02:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.82,0:02:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過在招待的賓客當中的確沒有您的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.14,0:02:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.90,0:02:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位先生是我請來的客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.90,0:02:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.55,0:02:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天下第一的名偵探毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.09,0:02:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是因為有人預謀殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.20,0:02:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才肯移駕到這裏來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.38,0:02:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.11,0:02:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花香殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.35,0:03:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我在幾天以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.65,0:03:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就收到這封恐嚇信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.82,0:03:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡之花將在海濱飯店綻放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.74,0:03:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是惡作劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.63,0:03:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個人就愛小題大作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.94,0:03:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管它就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.68,0:03:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.39,0:03:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是真的有個什麼萬一的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.82,0:03:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有準備的話還是比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.45,0:03:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看八成是那些嫉妒我得獎的酸葡萄幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.36,0:03:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些小家子氣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.96,0:03:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有時間浪費在他們身上呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.93,0:03:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.28,0:03:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡野利香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是前衛插花藝術家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.55,0:04:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還經常在電視上面出現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.76,0:04:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前衛插花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.34,0:04:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很厲害哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.86,0:04:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插花的時候還是含苞待放的花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.73,0:04:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會突然在一瞬間綻開哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.56,0:04:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像變魔術一樣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.84,0:04:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是變魔術就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.89,0:04:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來我可以說是藝術界的魔術師了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.43,0:04:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這女人還真惹人厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.58,0:04:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實老師的秘密在溫度上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.22,0:04:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白木經理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.11,0:04:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.33,0:04:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你收到一封無聊的恐嚇信是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.70,0:04:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不會有這種事情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.14,0:04:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的宴會是預定好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.83,0:04:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會因為這個有所變動吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.65,0:04:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.28,0:04:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您儘管放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.98,0:04:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是為我辦的宴會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.77,0:04:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切當然會照計畫進行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.81,0:04:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要是有個萬一的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.81,0:04:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是這個宴會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.68,0:04:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可別忘了這些日子在背後支持你的白木集團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.57,0:04:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.69,0:05:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼待會兒見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.56,0:05:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是討厭的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.55,0:05:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是這個飯店的經理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.22,0:05:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也對我們老師的前衛藝術讚賞有加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.79,0:05:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為有錢就了不起 可以買到藝術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.87,0:05:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看他那張臉就叫我覺得噁心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.72,0:05:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這盆花好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.96,0:05:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以調皮哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.58,0:05:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.21,0:05:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是液化氮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.71,0:05:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那種可以在瞬間冰凍的東西嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.29,0:05:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 你也知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.18,0:05:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是利香老師插花的秘訣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.81,0:05:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是利香老師想到這個的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.37,0:05:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者該說這是她發展出來的才比較妥當吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.95,0:05:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她發展出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.10,0:06:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個很不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.55,0:06:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 別這個樣子啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.12,0:06:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難看死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.75,0:06:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.22,0:06:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是名偵探毛利小五郎嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.44,0:06:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.14,0:06:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事情想拜託你可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.36,0:06:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間差不多了 所以我就來這兒叫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.55,0:06:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是都沒有回音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.94,0:06:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.31,0:06:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 有沒有備份鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.30,0:06:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,備份鑰匙在這兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.93,0:06:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白…白木經理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.94,0:06:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問一下 他脖子上的領帶是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.48,0:06:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們經理的領帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.41,0:07:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼看起來他應該是被勒死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.44,0:07:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這個屍體太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.81,0:07:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.88,0:07:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個小子 什麼時候跑進來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.55,0:07:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看這個領帶的結扣在前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.83,0:07:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.38,0:07:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 這麼說兇手是從被害人的正面把他給勒死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從背後勒還沒有話說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.74,0:07:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果從正面把他的脖子勒住的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.86,0:07:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都會強烈的抵抗才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.29,0:07:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.89,0:07:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被害人沒有任何抵抗的情況之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.07,0:07:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把被害人給勒死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.91,0:07:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他的力量應該很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.03,0:07:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.77,0:07:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是個塊頭很大的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.13,0:07:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這個人好像完全沒有抵抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.27,0:07:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.76,0:07:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管這個兇手勒他的力量再怎麼大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.54,0:07:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害人都應該會抵抗才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.51,0:07:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被勒得難受也許還會拉對方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.77,0:07:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是極力扯開領帶才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.18,0:07:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.48,0:07:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你們看被害人的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.66,0:07:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的指甲裏面什麼東西也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.29,0:07:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.65,0:08:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指甲裏面的確沒有任何的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.34,0:08:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 也不一定是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.95,0:08:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果以極大的力量勒住脖子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.23,0:08:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會讓人在一瞬間立刻就失去了意識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.67,0:08:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手果然是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.05,0:08:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔角選手那一種類型的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.53,0:08:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻派人調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.82,0:08:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在會場的賓客裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.85,0:08:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有類似這樣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.37,0:08:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太單純了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.54,0:08:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.36,0:08:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在鑑識課的人到達進行驗屍之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.43,0:08:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍體不要隨便移動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.11,0:08:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你怎麼還在這兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.96,0:08:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.08,0:08:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望跟負責這件事的警官說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.97,0:08:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.12,0:08:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件案子是由我負責的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.82,0:08:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是警視廳搜查一課的目暮警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.67,0:08:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白木經理被殺了對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.70,0:08:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你們現在打算怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.69,0:08:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然首先就是將這場宴會立刻取消
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.32,0:08:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.18,0:08:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經邀請了那麼多有頭有臉的賓客來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.41,0:08:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是取消的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.67,0:09:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我會造成很大損失的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.04,0:09:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.84,0:09:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說這話太自私了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我聽好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.52,0:09:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是一件預謀殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.71,0:09:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點我當然明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.68,0:09:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是兇手的目標又不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.45,0:09:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是白木經理對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.76,0:09:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們這些人就沒有危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.52,0:09:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話說的也沒錯啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.72,0:09:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這女人真夠自私的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.60,0:09:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.02,0:09:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為有錢就了不起 可以買到藝術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.23,0:09:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看他那張臉就叫我覺得噁心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.32,0:09:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.75,0:09:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過憑她的力量根本就不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.61,0:09:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.28,0:09:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在會場的賓客裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.61,0:09:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們發現有好幾個這樣的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.24,0:09:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個是職業摔角選手蟒蛇片桐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.56,0:09:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個是足球選手今村孝太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.92,0:09:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.00,0:09:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得叫蟒蛇片桐的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.15,0:09:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我們舉辦一場晚餐秀請他來參加的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.51,0:09:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就因為座位跟我們經理曾經發生過爭執
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.73,0:10:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定就是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.10,0:10:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對錯不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.46,0:10:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是這麼單純的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.98,0:10:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒什麼問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.21,0:10:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是岡野利香老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.74,0:10:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到世界藝術大獎的授獎紀念酒會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在場的各位來賓能夠抽空參加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.26,0:10:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本飯店在此由衷的感激
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.77,0:10:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.28,0:10:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟒蛇片桐先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.21,0:10:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能借一步問你幾句話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.98,0:10:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話待會兒再問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.99,0:10:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本還沒吃夠呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.64,0:10:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.09,0:10:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官 他有充分的不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.76,0:10:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.79,0:11:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 片桐先生到了會場之後一直跟他的幾個朋友在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.12,0:11:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點有很多人可以為他作證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.63,0:11:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官那裏出事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.19,0:11:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫你們快去幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.53,0:11:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏有淡淡的氯仿的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.35,0:11:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.00,0:11:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說利用這個讓人睡著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.06,0:11:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手無縛雞之力的人也能勒死人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.51,0:11:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過兇手是如何讓被害人聞到氯仿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.78,0:11:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這朵花好像不太對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.84,0:11:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪裏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.45,0:11:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.38,0:11:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得在休息室的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.39,0:11:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經理的那朵胸花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.38,0:11:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是合著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.70,0:11:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是現在卻綻開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.66,0:11:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是最好的賀禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.67,0:11:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.64,0:12:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實他只不過是我走向成功的一塊踏腳石而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.96,0:12:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過踏腳石畢竟是踏腳石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.92,0:12:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想要控制我根本是自不量力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.61,0:12:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 會被人家聽到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.31,0:12:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小翠 你只要乖乖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.85,0:12:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴巴閉緊做好我的助理就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.42,0:12:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是因為誰的緣故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.69,0:12:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才能混口飯吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.00,0:12:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我不該多嘴干涉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.63,0:12:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恐怖的女人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.14,0:12:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟 是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.37,0:12:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說差不多要上臺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.99,0:12:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.21,0:12:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 您可以準備上臺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.21,0:12:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.19,0:12:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是氯仿沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.18,0:13:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這另外一瓶是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.33,0:13:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氫氰酸矽化物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.89,0:13:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道兇手還想狙擊別的獵物嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.28,0:13:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她的目標到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.47,0:13:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是冰塊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.77,0:13:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是氯仿的冰塊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.44,0:13:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把冰凍的氯仿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.38,0:13:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在室溫之下慢慢的讓它溶化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.96,0:13:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能讓被害者吸入體內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.61,0:13:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且這次是使用氫氰酸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.67,0:13:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她會怎麼做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.51,0:13:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花瓣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.89,0:13:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很厲害哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.37,0:13:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插花的時候還是含苞待放的花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.28,0:13:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會突然在一瞬間綻開哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.49,0:13:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是利香老師插花的秘訣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.24,0:14:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.43,0:14:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來所有的秘密就藏在緊閉的花瓣裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.00,0:14:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她才要把花瓣冰住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.72,0:14:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手先把冰凍的氯仿藏在胸花的花瓣裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.14,0:14:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再急速的冷凍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.33,0:14:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來誰都不會產生懷疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.22,0:14:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裏每位賓客胸前都會佩帶一朵胸花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.87,0:14:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是花瓣在較高的室溫下溶化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.53,0:14:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢張開的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.61,0:14:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氯仿就揮發出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.55,0:14:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸入了氯仿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.21,0:14:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經理就陷入了昏迷狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.83,0:14:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手就能慢慢勒死他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.57,0:14:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是最好的賀禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.05,0:14:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.47,0:14:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果岡野利香就是兇手的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.03,0:14:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下一個目標到底會是誰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.26,0:14:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 我的厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.87,0:14:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下你們可知道了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.98,0:14:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利老弟別放手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.49,0:15:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼獵物戴的花應該是緊閉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.98,0:15:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要快點找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.37,0:15:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氫氰酸在攝氏25.7度就會揮發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.92,0:15:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到花開了的話就糟糕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.60,0:15:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位來賓 非常抱歉 讓各位久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.89,0:15:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡野利香世界藝術大會授獎紀念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.14,0:15:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,個人發表會現在開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.54,0:15:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.10,0:16:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰塊已經開始溶化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.02,0:16:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個溫度也在兇手的計算之內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.84,0:16:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.95,0:16:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有賓客戴的胸花是進會場的時候佩帶上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.97,0:16:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.22,0:16:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的花早就已經開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.72,0:16:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是我想太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.28,0:16:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標只有經理一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.57,0:16:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.65,0:16:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣兇手不會特意準備氫氰酸矽化物備用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.70,0:16:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手一定是想用那個再來謀殺什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.12,0:16:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.32,0:16:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.67,0:16:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.39,0:16:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很厲害哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.89,0:16:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插花的時候還是含苞待放的花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.83,0:16:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會突然在一瞬間綻開哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.93,0:16:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.85,0:16:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.91,0:16:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說她想自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.69,0:17:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.36,0:17:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.52,0:17:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.55,0:17:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.66,0:17:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.56,0:17:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個小鬼頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.83,0:17:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我最重要的一場表演給毀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.18,0:17:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.83,0:17:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.53,0:17:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我拿到它的時候就突然噴出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.93,0:17:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會在這兒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.16,0:17:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 你怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.97,0:17:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利老弟 你知道什麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.45,0:18:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是已經發現這件案子的線索在哪裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.80,0:18:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實真正讓這場表演中斷演出的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.80,0:18:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全是我的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.81,0:18:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.32,0:18:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣破壞我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.31,0:18:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會跟你善罷甘休的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.31,0:18:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊閉的花瓣綻放的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.85,0:18:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是你的生命必須要終結的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.72,0:18:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.89,0:18:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利老弟 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.86,0:18:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能解釋得清楚點讓大家都能聽懂呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.85,0:18:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.79,0:18:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你將這些用來插花的花全部密封
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.90,0:18:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了嚴防空氣滲透出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.76,0:18:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好是包個兩三層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.02,0:18:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這些花裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.61,0:18:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏著白木經理離奇死亡的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.72,0:18:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一件殺人未遂的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.19,0:18:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.69,0:18:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.35,0:18:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都包好了 毛利老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.14,0:18:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你可以說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.98,0:18:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是殺死經理白木先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.23,0:18:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是計畫殺害你的這一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.13,0:19:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是利用利香小姐前衛插花的主題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.35,0:19:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.99,0:19:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是緊閉的花瓣突然綻放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.88,0:19:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個方法來進行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.55,0:19:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說兇手就是岡野利香小姐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.53,0:19:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.90,0:19:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.67,0:19:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡說八道什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.62,0:19:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說我有什麼理由非要殺了白木經理呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.11,0:19:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 人不是你殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.10,0:19:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為兇手繼經理之後狙擊的目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.08,0:19:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.97,0:19:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.06,0:19:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人要殺我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.49,0:19:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底這個兇手是什麼人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.28,0:19:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人就是為白木經理別上胸花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.45,0:19:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還為表演的舞臺準備花材的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.28,0:19:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利香小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.20,0:19:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你應該很清楚了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.10,0:19:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.02,0:19:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是你的特別助理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.88,0:19:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾崎翠小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.22,0:19:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說小翠她要殺我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.04,0:19:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為唯一能夠在舞臺上整理花盆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.88,0:19:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了尾崎小姐之外 就別無他人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.18,0:19:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 如果尾崎小姐她就是兇手的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.20,0:19:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她安排的那些毒花也會把她自己毒死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.20,0:19:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.01,0:19:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的確是有輕生的念頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.15,0:20:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了能夠復仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.55,0:20:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情願與利香小姐一起犧牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.29,0:20:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.40,0:20:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.28,0:20:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的動機恐怕是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.31,0:20:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想動機應該是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.97,0:20:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者該說這是她發展出來的才比較妥當吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.18,0:20:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從尾崎小姐當時所說的這句話來推測
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.39,0:20:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初想到這種讓花綻放的前衛式插花的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.81,0:20:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不是岡野小姐才對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.02,0:20:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.58,0:20:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於白木經理還有她的作為我是忍無可忍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.80,0:20:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種前衛式插花是我姐姐小春想出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.89,0:20:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡野利香以前是她的學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.53,0:20:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她這個女人卻找了白木這個贊助人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.46,0:20:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她自己推舉成了創作前衛插花的第一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.08,0:20:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然在藝術界裏有實力的排擠沒有實力的是常有的現象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.07,0:20:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是岡野利香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.41,0:20:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她知道有我姐姐在她永遠沒有辦法出頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.65,0:20:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就用這種卑劣的手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.79,0:21:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟白木狼狽為奸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.16,0:21:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我姐姐不管到任何地方都不能發表她的作品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.26,0:21:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處施加壓力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.11,0:21:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.09,0:21:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種讓緊閉的花苞綻放的技巧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.53,0:21:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我姐姐自己苦思創造出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.86,0:21:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是利香她卻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.88,0:21:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後你姐姐怎麼樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.44,0:21:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她對於生命毫無留戀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.95,0:21:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就自己結束了生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.15,0:21:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡野利香 根本就沒有愛過這些花朵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.21,0:21:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是為了爭取名聲還有金錢利用它們罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.59,0:21:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我隱姓埋名做了你的助理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.96,0:21:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才真正瞭解到這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.07,0:21:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才更加不能放過你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.72,0:23:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件案子發生之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.29,0:23:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡野利香盜用別人構思的事實也同時公諸於世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.92,0:23:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以確定以後她將永遠無法再驕傲的站到眾人之前了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.72,0:23:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於我的下場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.91,0:23:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.10,0:23:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在對事情發展毫不知情的叔叔醒來之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.76,0:23:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就狠狠把我打了一頓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.17,0:23:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.54,0:23:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個強盜集團我想很有可能就在我們的身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.13,0:23:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那個人就是歹徒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.57,0:23:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.54,0:23:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.60,0:24:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人要你幫忙殺了那個姓赤羽的病人 對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.23,0:24:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.50,0:24:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,員警裏面也有他們的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.81,0:24:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.26,0:24:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶匪住院事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.76,0:24:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.36,0:24:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡芙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.21,0:24:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回是小五郎叔叔住院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.86,0:24:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧 目暮老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.80,0:24:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,by 高木警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.94,0:24:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
